'''大角縣'''（{{lang en|'''Big Horn County'''}}）是[[美國|美國]][[蒙大拿州|蒙大拿州]]南部的一個縣，南鄰[[懷俄明州|懷俄明州]]，面積12,988平方公里。根據[[美國2010年人口普查|2010年人口普查]]，本縣共有人口12,865人。<ref name=census>{{cite web|url=http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/SAFFPopulation?_event=Search&geo_id=05000US30009&_geoContext=01000US%7C04000US30%7C05000US30009&_street=&_county=Big+Horn&_cityTown=Big+Horn&_state=04000US30&_zip|title=Big Horn County, Montana|publisher=United States Census Bureau|accessdate=October 9, 2011|archive-url=https://archive.today/20200212053414/http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/SAFFPopulation?_event=Search&geo_id=05000US30009&_geoContext=01000US%7C04000US30%7C05000US30009&_street=&_county=Big+Horn&_cityTown=Big+Horn&_state=04000US30&_zip|archive-date=2020-02-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本縣縣治為[[哈丁_(蒙大拿州)|哈丁]]。{{GR|6}}

現在的縣成立於1913年1月13日。該州最早成立的其中一個縣[[卡斯特縣_(蒙大拿州)|卡斯特縣]]在成立時也與本縣同名，但後來於1877年改為現名。縣名來自當地常見的[[大角羊|大角羊]]。<ref>{{cite book|last=Merrill|first=Andrea|title=Montana almanac|url=https://archive.org/details/montanaalmanac0000merr_a1f5|year=1997|publisher=Falcon Publishing|location=Helena, Montana|isbn=1-56044-493-2|coauthors=Judy Jacobson|accessdate=2013-05-21|page=[https://archive.org/details/montanaalmanac0000merr_a1f5/page/7 7]}}</ref>  

== 地理 ==
[[File:Photo_of_Yellowtail_Dam,_Montana.jpeg|thumb]]
[[File:Little_Bighorn_cemetery_overview.jpg|thumb]]
根據[[2000年美国人口普查|2000年人口普查]]，大角縣的總面積為{{convert|5015|sqmi}}，其中有{{convert|4995|sqmi}}，即99.6%為陸地；{{convert|20|sqmi}}，即0.4%為水域。<ref>{{cite web
  |url=http://www.census.gov/tiger/tms/gazetteer/county2k.txt
  |title=Census 2000 U.S. Gazetteer Files: Counties
  |publisher=United States Census
  |accessdate=2011-02-13
  |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68EB8WXmf?url=http://www.census.gov/tiger/tms/gazetteer/county2k.txt
  |archive-date=2012-06-06
  |dead-url=yes
  }}</ref>本縣既是蒙大拿州面積第六大的縣份，亦是[[美國面積最大縣份列表|美國面積第64大的縣份]]。本縣大部份土地均由[[印第安人保留地|印第安人保留地]]組成。其中[[克羅印第安人保留地|克羅印第安人保留地]]佔了總面積的64.2%<ref>{{citation |chapterurl=http://digital.library.okstate.edu/Kappler/Vol1/HTML_files/MON0854.html |chapter=Montana: Crow Reserve |editor=Charles J. Kappler |location=Washington, DC |publisher=Government Printing Office |year=1904 |title=Indian Affairs: Laws and Treaties |accessdate=2013-05-21 |archive-date=2013-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520142216/http://digital.library.okstate.edu/Kappler/Vol1/HTML_files/MON0854.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，[[北夏安印第安人保留地|北夏安印第安人保留地]]則佔了6.37%。<ref>{{cite news|title=Northern Cheyenne voters split on resource development|url=http://billingsgazette.com/news/state-and-regional/montana/northern-cheyenne-voters-split-on-resource-development/article_c165f28d-7f1a-593a-8a8d-9e52f25c94e1.html|accessdate=17 January 2011|newspaper=billingsgazette.com|date=7 November 2006|archive-date=2012-07-10|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120710065701/http://billingsgazette.com/news/state-and-regional/montana/northern-cheyenne-voters-split-on-resource-development/article_c165f28d-7f1a-593a-8a8d-9e52f25c94e1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

